These are Puzzles for 1x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: iris, marigold, rose, aconite, begonia, sunflower
1. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
4. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
5. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |       2        |     3     |      4       |   5   |   6    |
| Flower   | marigold | begonia | iris | sunflower | aconite | rose |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-2::.
House: cottage, ranch-style, modern, gothic-revival, farmhouse, art-deco
1. the modern house is on the right of the cottage house##1
2. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
4. the modern house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
5. the cottage house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |   5    |    6    |
| House   | gothic-revival | cottage | modern | art-deco | farmhouse | ranch-style |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-3::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: red, lavender, azure, emerald, yellow, lilac
1. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
2. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
3. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes red##1
4. the person who likes lavender is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes emerald is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |   3    |    4     |       5       |       6       |
| Color   | lavender | azure | yellow | red | lilac | emerald |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-4::.
