.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-6::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: jet-ski, subway, trike, quad-bike, ship, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |     4     |   5    |    6    |
| Transport   | helicopter | quad-bike | subway | jet-ski | trike | ship |

