2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |    4     |   5    |     6     |
| Birthday   | november | july | january | may | august | october |

