.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-20::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, old-henry, davidoff, swisher, alhambra, blend
1. the swisher-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the blend-smoker is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
3. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
5. the blend-smoker is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
6. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4      |      5      |   6   |
| Cigar   | fonseca | davidoff | blend | alhambra | old-henry | swisher |

 